## 0: help (rc=0)
O 
O Usage: ufw COMMAND
O 
O Commands:
O  enable                          enables the firewall
O  disable                         disables the firewall
O  default ARG                     set default policy
O  logging LEVEL                   set logging to LEVEL
O  allow ARGS                      add allow rule
O  deny ARGS                       add deny rule
O  reject ARGS                     add reject rule
O  limit ARGS                      add limit rule
O  delete RULE|NUM                 delete RULE
O  insert NUM RULE                 insert RULE at NUM
O  prepend RULE                    prepend RULE
O  route RULE                      add route RULE
O  route delete RULE|NUM           delete route RULE
O  route insert NUM RULE           insert route RULE at NUM
O  reload                          reload firewall
O  reset                           reset firewall
O  status                          show firewall status
O  status numbered                 show firewall status as numbered list of RULES
O  status verbose                  show verbose firewall status
O  show ARG                        show firewall report
O  version                         display version information
O 
O Application profile commands:
O  app list                        list application profiles
O  app info PROFILE                show information on PROFILE
O  app update PROFILE              update PROFILE
O  app default ARG                 set default application policy
O 
